== 赛程概况 ==
=== 资格赛 ===
1984年4月1至14日<ref name="F5Ph8">{{cite news | title = For the record | newspaper = [[泰晤士报|The Times]] | page = 22 | date = 1984-04-02}}</ref><ref name="vfmzg">{{cite news | title = For the record | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 31 | date = 1984-04-14}}</ref>，本届世锦赛的资格赛在[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]雷德伍德洛奇（{{lang|en|Redwood Lodge}}）举行，共78人参加<ref name="EVERTON" /><ref name="CUEQ">{{cite news | title = Qualifying rounds summary | work = Cue World | location = Mitcham Junction | publisher = Transworld Publications | date = 1984-05 | page = 23}}</ref>。所有选手分成16组，经淘汰赛选出16人进入正式比赛。淘汰赛均采用19局10胜制。[[汤米·墨菲|汤米·墨菲]]（{{lang|en|Tommy Murphy}}）首轮打出两次单杆108分并淘汰[[杰克·菲茨莫里斯|杰克·菲茨莫里斯]]（{{lang|en|Jack Fitzmaurice}}），两周前他还在[[世界撞球錦標賽_(英式撞球)|世界职业台球锦标赛]]决赛战胜菲茨莫里斯<ref name="2TONSMURHPHY">{{cite news | title = Snooker | work = Aberdeen Press and Journal | page = 13 | date = 1984-04-03}}</ref>。[[約翰·帕洛特|約翰·帕洛特]]三轮比赛先后以十比三、十比二和十比零淘汰[[丹尼斯·休斯|丹尼斯·休斯]]（{{lang|en|Dennis Hughes}}）、[[克里夫·艾佛頓|克里夫·艾佛頓]]和[[1978年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1978年世锦赛]]亚军[[佩里·芒斯|佩里·芒斯]]（{{lang|en|Perrie Mans}}）<ref name="EVERTON" />。年仅20岁的英国少年斯诺克冠军[[尼尔·富尔兹|尼尔·富尔兹]]（{{lang|en|Neal Foulds}}）从资格赛首度晋级克鲁西布剧院世锦赛正式比赛<ref name="XOlAf">{{cite news | title = Sport in brief | newspaper = [[衛報|The Guardian]] | location = London | page = 22 | date = 1984-04-06}}</ref><ref name="spor_Worl">{{Cite web | title = World Snooker Championship memories from ITV and Eurosport pundit Neal Foulds | work = Sporting Life | access-date = 2021-03-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201011005543/https://www.sportinglife.com/snooker/news/1984-world-championship-stands-out/179173 | url = https://www.sportinglife.com/snooker/news/1984-world-championship-stands-out/179173 | archive-date = 2020-10-11}}</ref>，三轮资格赛分别以十比五、十比四和十比二淘汰[[道格·法兰奇|道格·法兰奇]]（{{lang|en|Doug French}}）、[[莱斯·多德|莱斯·多德]]（{{lang|en|Les Dodd}}）与[[吉姆·梅多克罗夫特|吉姆·梅多克罗夫特]]（{{lang|en|Jim Meadowcroft}}）<ref name="EVERTON" />。

八获世界冠军的[[佛雷德·戴維斯|佛雷德·戴維斯]]以十比五击败[[吉姆·唐纳利|吉姆·唐纳利]]（{{lang|en|Jim Donnelly}}）<ref name="EVERTON" /><ref name="Hq4qT">{{cite news | title = Break of 82 restores Taylor's confidence | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 22 | date = 1984-04-24}}</ref>。加拿大选手[[约翰·贝尔_(台球)|约翰·贝尔]]（{{lang|en|John Bear}}）没有按时参赛，对手[[罗伊·安德鲁塔|罗伊·安德鲁塔]]（{{lang|en|Roy Andrewartha}}）[[自動當選|自动晋级]]<ref name="EVERTON" />。[[迈克·沃特森|迈克·沃特森]]（{{lang|en|Mike Watterson}}）是1977至1983年世锦赛推广人，也是他率先选定克鲁西布剧院作为比赛场地<ref name="GRAUN20MAR19">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Mike Watterson obituary | url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/mar/20/mike-watterson-obituary | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | date = 2019-03-20 | access-date = 2021-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108034919/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/mar/20/mike-watterson-obituary | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="GRAUN28APR83">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Higgins recovers to show the champion's touch | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | date = 1983-04-28 | page = 24}}</ref>，他在首轮以十比五战胜[[伯纳德·贝内特|伯纳德·贝内特]]（{{lang|en|Bernard Bennett}}），但很快就以八比十不敌[[沃伦·金|沃伦·金]]（{{lang|en|Warren King}}）<ref name="EVERTON" />。资格赛淘汰选手可获450英镑参与奖<ref name="MONEY" />。安德鲁塔、富尔兹、帕洛特、金、[[马塞尔·高维罗|马塞尔·高维罗]]（{{lang|en|Marcel Gauvreau}}）、[[乔·约翰逊_(斯诺克球手)|乔·约翰逊]]、[[保罗·米夫苏德|保罗·米夫苏德]]（{{lang|en|Paul Mifsud}}）、[[马里奥·莫拉_(台球)|马里奥·莫拉]]（{{lang|en|Mario Morra}}）和[[埃迪·辛克莱|埃迪·辛克莱]]（{{lang|en|Eddie Sinclair}}）都是首次参加世锦赛资格赛<ref name="g2wtu">{{Cite news | title = Mersey aces cue up for glory | work = Liverpool Echo | date = 1984-04-18 | page = 38}}</ref>。

=== 正式赛首轮 ===
首轮正式赛在4月21至26日举行<ref>{{cite magazine | title = Embassy World Snooker Championship | magazine = Snooker Scene | location = Birmingham | publisher = Everton's News Agency | date = 1984-06 | pages = 1–10}}</ref>，每局都是资格赛晋级选手对抗种子选手，采用19局10胜制，共分两[[撞球術語列表|阶段]]<ref name="Global Snooker" />。[[大卫·泰勒|大卫·泰勒]]（{{lang|en|David Taylor}}）首阶段结束时以三比五落后高维罗，但第二阶段开始后连赢七局以十比五胜出，这还是他在1983至1984年赛季首次赢得排名赛<ref name="YSkdh">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Taylor breaks back in style: Snooker | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 20 | date = 1984-04-24}}</ref>。安德鲁塔正职从事[[碼錶時間研究|碼錶時間研究]]，斯诺克只是业余爱好，在首轮以四比十负于[[埃迪·查尔顿|埃迪·查尔顿]]（{{lang|en|Eddie Charlton}}）<ref name="aKS6a" />。富尔兹在首阶段结束时以五比三领先前世界冠军希金斯，双方竞争激烈，第二阶段打成七平后最终由富尔兹以十比九晋级<ref name="aKS6a">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Giant-killing Foulds breaks into the elite: Snooker | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 22 | date = 1984-04-25}}</ref>。

[[西尔维诺·弗朗西斯科|西尔维诺·弗朗西斯科]]（{{lang|en|Silvino Francisco}}）以十比五战胜此时在全季斯诺赛巡回赛收入排名第四的[[托尼·米奥|托尼·米奥]]（{{lang|en|Tony Meo}}）<ref name="4cvGP">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Francisco sets up Reardon rematch: Snooker | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 15 | date = 1984-04-23}}</ref>。[[威利·索恩|威利·索恩]]（{{lang|en|Willie Thorne}}）击败[[约翰·维尔戈|约翰·维尔戈]]（{{lang|en|John Virgo}}），上届世锦赛维尔戈同样输在索恩手里<ref name="3mI1M">{{cite news | title = Mountjoy promise | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 24 | date = 1984-04-26}}</ref>，而且本赛季还没赢过排名赛，世界排名从16掉至18<ref name="HxNyP">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = White moves up but Davis out on his own:: Snooker | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 29 | date = 1984-05-09}}</ref>。八获世界冠军的弗雷德·戴维斯在首轮以四比十不敌[[比尔·温本纽克|比尔·温本纽克]]（{{lang|en|Bill Werbeniuk}}），这是他最后一次参加世锦赛。他曾于[[1937年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1937年]]首度参赛，此时年纪70岁253天，创下世锦赛球员年龄新纪录。<ref name="urEMP">{{cite web | last = Turner | first = Chris | title = Various Snooker Records | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/Records.html | website = Chris Turner's Snooker Archive | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160519094601/http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/Records.html | archive-date = 2016-05-19 | access-date = 2016-05-19 }}</ref>

众多比赛呈一边倒局面：[[丹尼斯·泰勒|丹尼斯·泰勒]]与[[柯克·史蒂文斯|柯克·史蒂文斯]]（{{lang|en|Kirk Stevens}}）均以十比一晋级；[[泰瑞·格里菲斯|泰瑞·格里菲斯]]以十比二胜出；[[史蒂夫·戴维斯|史蒂夫·戴维斯]]、[[約翰·史賓塞_(英國運動員)|约翰·斯宾塞]]和[[克里夫·索本|克里夫·索本]]以十比三获胜；温本纽克、[[道格·芒特乔伊|道格·芒特乔伊]]（{{lang|en|Doug Mountjoy}}）与查尔顿以十比四进入下一轮。四名种子选手在首轮淘汰，分别是四号种子[[托尼·诺尔斯|托尼·诺尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tony Knowles}}）、五号种子希金斯、14号种子维尔戈与15号种子米奥。<ref name="SNSREP">{{cite magazine | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Embassy World Snooker Championship | magazine = Snooker Scene | pages = 5–17 | publisher = Everton's News Agency | location = Birmingham | date = 1984-06}}</ref>

史蒂夫·戴维斯过去三年打入世锦赛后只在[[1982年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1982年]]首轮败给诺尔斯，但诺尔斯今年在首轮以七比十不敌帕洛特。此前《[[太陽報_(英國)|太阳报]]》刊登访谈诺尔斯的三段式报道，他在接受采访时吹嘘性经历，对其他参赛选手嗤之以鼻。<ref name="TPuYR">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Sun sets on Knowles | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 20 | date = 1984-04-27}}</ref>世界职业台球与斯诺克协会为此向诺尔斯罚款五千英镑，理由是他的言行令斯诺克运动蒙羞<ref name="EVERTON" />。

二号种子[[雷·里尔顿|雷·里尔顿]]以十比七战胜[[吉姆·威奇|吉姆·威奇]]（{{lang|en|Jim Wych}}），[[吉米·怀特|吉米·怀特]]以十比六击败[[雷克斯·威廉士|雷克斯·威廉士]]，不过威廉士在第12局打出单杆138分，不但是本届世锦赛单杆最高分，还是第一个单杆破百分<ref name="33zVj">{{cite news | title = Higgins ousted by newcomer in world championship upset | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 24 | date = 1984-04-25}}</ref>。第一轮16组选手理论上最多需打304局，实际只打233局，平均每局22.5分钟。持续时间最长的一局是索本与莫拉交手，花费51分钟，最短的是怀特与威廉士对抗，只用九分钟。<ref name="WA9As">{{cite magazine | last = Hale | first = Janice | title = Crucible Diary | magazine = Snooker Scene | date = 1984-06 | publisher = Everton's News Agency | location = Birmingham | page = 10}}</ref>

=== 第二轮 ===
第二轮正式赛于4月26至30日举行，采用25局13胜制，分为三阶段<ref name="4cvGP" />。史蒂夫·戴维斯以六比四领先斯宾塞后在接下来八局拿下七局，以13比5晋级，其中三局打出单杆100、95和92分<ref name="cOBVd">{{cite news | title = Davis takes charge with 100 break | newspaper = The Times | page = 29 | date = 1984-04-28}}</ref>。怀特在首阶段结束时以三比五落后查尔顿，但第二阶段只输一局并打出单杆80、79、44、61、34和82分，以十比六反超，第三阶段前四局又拿下三局，以13比7获胜。格里菲斯以13比5打败温本纽克。<ref name="jXrtt">{{cite news | title = Brilliant White moves on | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 19 | date = 1984-04-30}}</ref>

丹尼斯·泰勒在前两阶段结束时以11比7领先帕洛特，但帕洛特在第三阶段开始后连下四局打成11平。泰勒顶住压力稳定发挥，连赢两局以13比11晋级。索本与索恩的比赛竞争激烈，最后索本以13比11打入八强。<ref name="IJcZf">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Taylor survives late flutter by Parrott | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/23 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 23 | date = 1984-05-01}}</ref>史蒂文斯与大卫·泰勒打成九平后稳定发挥，三次打出单杆超过50分，以13比10淘汰对手。富尔兹一度以三比一领先芒特乔伊，但最后以6比13失利。<ref name="Iw06I">{{cite news | last = Hale | first = Janice | title = Right on cue, 'Sheffield' the snooker soap opera gets an X certificate | newspaper = [[觀察家報|The Observer]] | page = 39 | date = 1984-04-29}}</ref>

里尔顿在本赛季职业斯诺克比赛的表现比过去16年都差，首阶段结束时他以五比三领先弗朗西斯科，其中第八局还打出单杆109分，第二阶段结束时双方打成八平。弗朗西斯科在第三阶段开始后一度领先，但在薄蓝球时失手，里尔顿只需做成一次斯诺克就能反超比分。里尔顿做斯诺克后弗朗西斯科犯规，里尔顿加分后拿下这局以九比八领先，随后又连下四盘，以13比8结束战斗。<ref name="hhtdG">{{cite magazine | title = Reardon beat Francisco 13–8 | magazine = Snooker Scene | date = 1984-06 | location = Birmingham | publisher = Everton's News Agency | page = 14}}</ref>

=== 八强 ===
[[File:Dennis_Taylor,_2004.jpg|thumb]]（图）在八强赛以13比8战胜道格·芒特乔伊]]

5月1至2日的八强赛同样分三阶段，25局13胜制<ref name="4cvGP" />。史蒂夫·戴维斯首阶段先下三局，但格里菲斯连追五局反超；第二阶段开始后格里菲斯先下一城，但戴维斯还以颜色追到六平，第二阶段结束时双方打成八平<ref name="yr7Xj">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Griffiths keeps pressure on Davis | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/19 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 19 | date = 1984-05-02}}</ref>。戴维斯在第三阶段前七局拿下五局，以13比10打入四强，新闻报道称赞双方技艺高超、稳扎稳打<ref name="FIREWORKS">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Fireworks in blue suede shoes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/26 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 26 | date = 1984-05-03}}</ref>。

史蒂文斯与里尔顿的八强赛首阶段提前一局结束，只赢一局的里尔顿表示“终于结束了”<ref name="quarterSS">{{cite magazine | title = Quarter-finals | magazine = Snooker Scene | first = Clive | last = Everton | page = 15 | location = Birmingham | publisher = Everton's News Agency | date = 1984-06}}</ref>。史蒂文斯最后在第二盘就结束比赛，以13比2大胜里尔顿，后者只拿下第一和第九局<ref name="quarterSS" />。怀特在第二阶段结束时以十比六领先索本，最后以13比8晋级。怀特在第20局先得63分，索本接手后清台打出64分反败为胜，但怀特把握赛点在第21局胜出，准备在半决赛与史蒂文斯交手。<ref name="quarterSS" />丹尼斯·泰勒同样以13比8击败芒特乔伊，半决赛对手是戴维斯<ref name="FIREWORKS" />。

=== 四强 ===
5月3至5日的四强赛采用31局16胜制，分为四阶段<ref name="4cvGP" />。史蒂夫·戴维斯首阶段结束时以四比三领先丹尼斯·泰勒，泰勒所赢三局有两局是靠最后的黑球翻盘<ref name="SnookerScene">{{cite magazine | title = Semi-finals | magazine = Snooker Scene | first = Clive | last = Everton | page = 17 | date = 1984-06}}</ref>。第二阶段戴维斯先赢三局，泰勒马上追回两局。第13局泰勒单杆打到64分时击红球失手，结果戴维斯打出65分反超，下一局又打出单杆76分，第二阶段结束时以九比五领先<ref name="SnookerScene" /><ref name="TAYNO">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Taylor without answers as Davis nears another final | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/30 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 30 | date = 1984-05-05}}</ref>。第三阶段前五局泰勒只赢一局，但他马上追回两局，避免比赛在第三阶段结束<ref name="SnookerScene" />。第四阶段开局后，戴维斯在前四局拿下三局，以16比9晋级决赛<ref name="SnookerScene" /><ref name="DAVUND">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Davis undermines White's confidence | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/16 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 16 | date = 1984-05-07}}</ref>。

史蒂文斯靠做斯诺克拿下第一局，但怀特随后连赢三局<ref name="SnookerScene" />。怀特在前一晚庆祝22岁生日狂欢，此时很不舒服<ref name="SnookerScene" />，第五局打出单杆85分时还因不适暂停比赛，首阶段结束时他以五比三领先。怀特估计他是因吃的三明治有问题生病，而且用来治疗咽喉炎的止咳糖浆同样令身体不适。<ref name="SnookerScene" /><ref name="TAYNO" /><ref name="Ogmwj">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = White ahead after a sandwich nearly upsets his big break | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/22 | newspaper = The Times | page = 22 | date = 1984-05-04}}</ref>第二阶段前七局只花费90分钟出头，双方打成六平，结束时史蒂文斯以八比七反超<ref name="SnookerScene" /><ref name="TAYNO" />。第三阶段时怀特不良反应加重，步履都有些蹒跚，史蒂文斯连赢三局<ref name="SnookerScene" />，但怀特又追回三局，结束时史蒂文斯以12比10领先<ref name="SnookerScene" />。史蒂文斯在第23局击打红球时失误，怀特发力连下五城以15比12反超拿到赛点<ref name="SnookerScene" />。史蒂文斯此后虽追回两局，但怀特以单杆44分拿下第30局<ref name="SnookerScene" />，总比分16比14晋级决赛，成为世锦赛历史上最年轻的决赛选手<ref name="DAVUND" /><ref name="WWU">{{cite news | last = Hale | first = Janice | date = 1984-05-06 | title = White wakes up the Crucible | newspaper = The Observer | location = London | page = 35}}</ref>。

=== 决赛 ===
[[File:Steve_Davis_PHC_2012-1.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2012年）在决赛以18比16战胜[[吉米·怀特|吉米·怀特]]顺利卫冕，这是他第三次拿下世锦赛冠军]]

决赛在5月6至7日举行，采用35局18胜制并分四阶段，卫冕冠军史蒂夫·戴维斯迎战吉米·怀特<ref name="4cvGP" /><ref name="IT">{{Cite news | title = My sporting disappointment: Jimmy White and the elusive World Championship | first = Keith | last = Duggan | newspaper = [[爱尔兰时报|The Irish Times]] | date = 2020-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301193206/https://www.irishtimes.com/sport/other-sports/my-sporting-disappointment-jimmy-white-and-the-elusive-world-championship-1.4325847 | access-date = 2021-03-03 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.irishtimes.com/sport/other-sports/my-sporting-disappointment-jimmy-white-and-the-elusive-world-championship-1.4325847 | archive-date = 2021-03-01}}</ref>。比赛由英格兰裁判吉姆·索普（{{lang|en|Jim Thorpe}}）主持，是他在[[1980年斯诺克英国锦标赛|1980]]和[[1984年斯诺克英国锦标赛|1984年]][[斯诺克英国锦标赛|斯诺克英国锦标赛]]后第三次主持[[斯诺克三大赛|三大赛]]决赛<ref name="yoYz6">{{Cite web | title = Triple Crown Final Referees | work = [[世界职业台球与斯诺克协会|World Snooker]] | access-date = 2021-03-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210110205703/https://wst.tv/corporate/referees/triple-crown-final-referees/ | url = https://wst.tv/corporate/referees/triple-crown-final-referees/ | archive-date = 2021-01-10}}</ref>。

戴维斯首阶段结束时以六比一领先，第二阶段又拿下前两局<ref name="Glasgow1">{{Cite news | title = Davis dominates White in world title decider | newspaper = The Glasgow Herald | access-date = 2021-03-03 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=48NAAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_aUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=5219%2C1660783 | date = 1984-05-07 | via = Google news | archive-date = 2020-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201023212749/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=48NAAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_aUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=5219,1660783 }}</ref>。怀特以单杆过50分拿下第十局，但第二阶段中场休息时仍以二比十大比分落后<ref name="Glasgow1" />。接下来怀特追回两局，可第15局又在母球失误落袋后失利，戴维斯再接再励赢得下一局，第二阶段结束时以12比4领先<ref name="IT" /><ref name="DAVUND" />。次日怀特发力，在第三阶段八局只输一局，比分追至11比13<ref name="1cAXt">{{cite news | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Davis retains world title after enthralling battle with White | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_los-angeles-times_1984-05-05/page/25 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 25 | date = 1984-05-08}}</ref>。2020年，戴维斯在接受采访时表示，当年决赛在第一天比赛后领先八局，导致他有些得意忘形<ref name="bbc._Hend">{{Cite news | title = Hendry & Davis relive Crucible Classics | last1 = Phillips | first1 = Owen | last2 = Hafez | first2 = Shamoon | work = [[BBC體育|BBC Sport]] | date = 2020-04-17 | access-date = 2021-03-03 | url = https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/52294986 | archive-date = 2021-02-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210212231850/https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/52294986}}</ref>。第四阶段开始后戴维斯打出单杆119分，是本届世锦赛单杆第二高分，他在前四局拿下三局，以16比12领先。怀特连追三局追到15比16，但接下来的第32局又是戴维斯清完彩色球后反超并拿到赛点。怀特第33局以单杆65分胜出，但戴维斯在第34局以77比40获胜，总比分18比16，成为克鲁西布剧院历史上首位连庄世锦赛冠军。<ref name="1cAXt" /><ref name="GGQ3J">{{cite news | title = 1984: Davis outshines White | date = 2003-04-18 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953919.stm | work = [[BBC體育|BBC Sport]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107024947/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953919.stm | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-01-07 | access-date = 2021-03-03}}</ref><ref name="Glasgow">{{cite news | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ygI-AAAAIBAJ&pg=6771%2C1950439 | title = Boos as Davis retains crown | date = 1984-05-08 | newspaper = The Glasgow Herald | access-date = 2021-03-03 | via = Google news}}</ref>

这是戴维斯继1981和1983年后第三次获世锦赛冠军，怀特是世锦赛历史上最年轻的决赛选手，但在不敌戴维斯后五次打入世锦赛决赛均未胜出<ref name="9Z1CL">{{cite web | last = Turner | first = Chris | title = World Professional Championship | url = http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/world.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160606102115/http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/world.html | archive-date = 2016-06-06 | work = cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk | publisher = Chris Turner's Snooker Archive | access-date = 2016-06-06}}</ref><ref name="WWU" />。如果打败戴维斯，怀特就能打破希金斯的纪录，成为世锦赛历史上最年轻的冠军<ref name="Uw2IK">{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | date = 1984-05-08 | title = Davis thwarts White's comeback | newspaper = The Guardian | location = London | page = 23}}</ref>。戴维斯拿到4.4万英镑冠军奖金，1983至1984年赛季拿到的奖金总额达到15万9511英镑，比第二名怀特的7万8725英镑高一倍多<ref name="Gkv1I" />。世界排名在赛后更新，戴维斯排第一，怀特第七，后者在1983至1984年赛季一共拿到17分，其中本届世锦赛亚军就占八分<ref name="o8RMV">{{cite magazine | title = How they stand: official world rankings 1985 | magazine = Snooker Scene | pages = 18–19 | location = Birmingham | publisher = Everton's News Agency | date = 1984-06}}</ref>。

{{quotebox|“我当时充满信心，觉得下一年肯定能赢，要不然就再过一年，所以对当时失利感觉无所谓。”|source=吉米·怀特回忆本届世锦赛<ref name="IT" />}}

戴维斯打败人气高涨的怀特后，观众发出嘘声和嘲笑声<ref name="Glasgow" />。他自认决赛最后一天表现不及对手，但已竭尽全力<ref name="Glasgow" />。戴维斯此后两年都打入决赛，在20世纪80年代还会三获世锦赛冠军<ref name="euro_Emot">{{Cite web | title = Emotional Steve Davis announces retirement after glorious 38-year career | first = Desmond | last = Kane | work = Eurosport UK | date = 2016-04-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031021543/https://www.eurosport.co.uk/snooker/emotional-steve-davis-announces-retirement-after-glorious-38-year-career_sto5448403/story.shtml | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | url = https://www.eurosport.co.uk/snooker/emotional-steve-davis-announces-retirement-after-glorious-38-year-career_sto5448403/story.shtml | access-date = 2021-03-03}}</ref><ref name="news_BBCS">{{Cite news | title = 1989: Davis makes it six | work = [[BBC體育|BBC Sport]] | date = 2004-04-07 | access-date = 10 October 2020 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/other_sports/snooker/3557655.stm | archive-date = 2004-04-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040426011003/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/other_sports/snooker/3557655.stm }}</ref>。怀特自认此前半决赛战胜史蒂文斯后非常疲惫，所以决赛第一天表现不佳<ref name="Glasgow" />。截至2020年，怀特共六次打入世锦赛决赛，但从未胜出<ref name="sund_Down">{{Cite news | title = Down memory lane: Crucible was theatre of nightmares for Jimmy White | first = John | last = Barrett | newspaper = The Sunday Post | access-date = 2021-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201011114910/https://www.sundaypost.com/fp/down-memory-lane-crucible-was-theatre-of-nightmares-for-jimmy-white/ | archive-date = 2020-10-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.sundaypost.com/fp/down-memory-lane-crucible-was-theatre-of-nightmares-for-jimmy-white/}}</ref><ref name="wst._Whit">{{Cite web | title = White Crowned Senior Champion | work = World Snooker | date = 2010-11-19 | access-date = 2021-03-03 | url = https://wst.tv/white-crowned-senior-champion/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017021516/https://wst.tv/white-cr